1. Moj prijatelj uči *jezik* japanskog. (My friend is learning the *language* of Japanese.)
2. Jezikom životinja bave se zoologija i etologija. (*Language* of animals is studied by zoology and ethology.)
3. *Jezik* mi se zapetljao dok sam pokušavao da objasnim svoje mišljenje. (My *tongue* got tangled while I was trying to explain my opinion.)
4. Hrvatski *jezik* mi je maternji, a srpski jezik znam takođe. (Croatian *language* is my mother tongue, and I also know Serbian *language*.)
5. Postoji mnogo stranih *jezika* koje bismo mogli naučiti. (There are many foreign *languages* that we could learn.)
6. Međunarodni dan maternjeg *jezika* se obeležava 21. februara. (International Mother Language Day is celebrated on February 21st.)
7. Ona je izuzetno vešta u poznavanju *jezika*, govori pet stranih jezika. (She is extremely skilled in *language* knowledge, she speaks five foreign languages.)
8. Učim *jezik* od svoje šeste godine i sada sam veoma dobar u tome. (I have been learning a *language* since I was six years old and now I am very good at it.)
9. Srpski *jezik* ima dva pisma - ćirilicu i latinicu. (Serbian *language* has two scripts - Cyrillic and Latin.)
10. *Jezik* jezika menja se tokom vremena i pod uticajem kulture. (*Language* of language changes over time and under the influence of culture.)